---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import GridItem from "../components/GridItem.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title='Home'>
  <section class='w-screen grid md:grid-cols-2 p-8 pt-0 md:pt-8 pb-16'>
    <div class='flex hero text-white md:h-[30vw] p-8 md:p-0'>
      <div class='my-auto md:ml-8 select-none'>
        <h1 class='text-8xl font-bold'>SOY XXVI</h1>
        <h3 class='flex gap-3 items-center text-2xl mt-2'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-location-dot'></i><span>Levi, Lapland</span>
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='md:mx-16 md:my-auto mt-16'>
      <h1 class='text-4xl mb-8'>Lapland Course</h1>
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Veniam enim
        molestias qui deserunt culpa amet numquam, facilis blanditiis earum
        laboriosam consectetur corporis soluta ut eius est voluptate, neque
        quasi provident voluptates quod! Quia beatae voluptates ea distinctio
        tenetur explicabo quidem natus rerum eligendi aut ratione quis
        reprehenderit, inventore incidunt nihil rem, saepe officia debitis
        sapiente consequatur veritatis eveniet illum delectus iste. Aliquam
        omnis eum magni nemo, voluptatum tempora quos laborum hic optio dolor,
        dolores ipsa laboriosam totam aperiam placeat, quas iusto eveniet natus
        ipsum officia! Accusantium natus provident minus sint ea mollitia, quia,
        corporis consequatur possimus doloremque, dolores at iure.
      </p>
      <button class='mt-4'>
        <a href='/registration'>Register</a>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class='mx-16 grid xl:grid-cols-3 gap-6 xl:gap-0 grid-flow-dense'>
    <GridItem
      icon='fa-solid fa-brain'
      title='big brains'
      body='mir sind eif so schlau'
    />
    <GridItem
      icon='fa-solid fa-house'
      title='comfy'
      body='fühl dich wie dihei'
    />
    <GridItem
      icon='fa-solid fa-cross'
      title='ka'
      body='was ich da ane söt schribe'
    />
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background-image: url("../assets/hero-bg.jpg");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
</style>
